@startuml unnmdnwb3_dora

actor "DevOps User" as User
participant "API (Gin-Gonic)" as API
participant "Metrics Calculation Service" as MetricsService
participant "GitLab Connector" as GitLabConnector
participant "Prometheus Connector" as PrometheusConnector
database "MongoDB" as MongoDB
participant "GitLab" as GitLab
participant "Prometheus" as Prometheus

User -> API: Request DORA metrics
activate API

API -> MetricsService: Calculate metrics
activate MetricsService

MetricsService -> GitLabConnector: Fetch data (commits, pipelines)
activate GitLabConnector
GitLabConnector -> GitLab: API requests
GitLab --> GitLabConnector: Response
GitLabConnector --> MetricsService: GitLab data
deactivate GitLabConnector

MetricsService -> PrometheusConnector: Fetch alert data
activate PrometheusConnector
PrometheusConnector -> Prometheus: Query alerts
Prometheus --> PrometheusConnector: Alert data
PrometheusConnector --> MetricsService: Prometheus data
deactivate PrometheusConnector

MetricsService -> MongoDB: Store raw data
MongoDB --> MetricsService: Confirmation

MetricsService -> MetricsService: Aggregate data
MetricsService -> MetricsService: Calculate DORA metrics

MetricsService -> MongoDB: Store calculated metrics
MongoDB --> MetricsService: Confirmation

MetricsService --> API: Calculated metrics
deactivate MetricsService

API --> User: DORA metrics response
deactivate API

@enduml